aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:02.850
Episode Duapuluh

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:02.850
Sebuah Mimpi Mabuk Kesombongan...

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:02.850
(Bagian Dua)

